DPSR-Specific Targeting We target exclusively doubly-shadowed craters (~25K) rather than all 
PSRs (~110K). The 85K temperature difference dramatically increases 
ice stability and preservation. Most teams will analyse all PSR craters; 
we focus on the 4 DPSR craters ISRO's own paper identified — a 
